  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Hotel Magic is offered on a half board basis with breakfast and dinner served in the hotels restaurant.</p>
<p>Breakfast consists of a continental hot and cold buffet.</p>
<p>Dinner is a buffet style meal with good choice of main courses along with starter, salad and dessert buffets.</p>
<p>A new Year gala dinner included with unlimited cava diring dinner and a gift.</p>
<p> </p>
<p>Pre-book the Ski Inclusive package and in addition to lift passes and skis and boots, lunch vouchers are included for 6 lunches (sandwich, chips and a drink) on the mountain at participating restaurants.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
