  <description><![CDATA[<p>This quality 4 star hotel has already established itself as a Pas family favourite. The hotel has very stylish interiors with a relaxed atmosphere, comfortable lounges and well furnished attractive bedrooms.</p>
<h2>Fantastic location </h2>
<p>Hotel Magic is in a fantastic location, right in the middle of resort, so you'll be able to go out and explore the shops and restaurants when you're not up on the slopes. The hotel is also located near the après ski scene with a range of bars only a short walk away. The ski lifts and ski school meeting point are 150 metres from the hotel and there is also a bus stop located just outside that will take you towards <a data-udi="umb://document/7bd0ea2aff2942389cbf8acdba0a0e77" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7bd0ea2aff2942389cbf8acdba0a0e77}" title="Soldeu">Soldeu</a> and the capital, Andorra la Vella.</p>
<h2>Water area </h2>
<p>Hotel Magic's water area is a firm favourite with guests and provides some wonderful relaxation facilities. You'll find a hot tub and sauna at your disposal as well as a fitness room and reading room. There is also the opportunity to book a local massage with one of the hotels specialists, if your muscles get too sore.</p>]]></description>
