  <locationDescription><![CDATA[<p>The hotel is located right in the heart of Pas de la Casa and close to après-ski bars and the village nightlife.</p>
<p>It is under a 2 minutes' walk (150 metres) to the ski lifts and slopes.</p>
<p>The ski hire shop and ski school meeting place are close to the main lifts.</p>
